{"tid":1754111,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"重奪立法會控制權先係最終目標","createTime":"2019-11-25T06:06:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T06:09:15.000Z","uid":338458,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6d05bc1766e0edfd645a9ac1c2c0e4813edefc5b","tid":1754111,"uid":338458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T06:06:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">首先多謝咁多位手足，令區選贏左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">但重奪立法會控制權先係打大佬</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">只要贏左立法會，到時蒙面法，23條通通都唔洗過，<br />\n泛民都唔洗再拉布，因為可以否決<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋我好想睇下柒婆同泛民食飯，冷落建制派<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">只要拎返個控制權先對得住死左嘅手足，5000位拉左嘅手足，受過傷嘅手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n經過呢戰，建制派一定會更比力種票，𠝹票，蛇齋餅粽呃d公公婆婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地要做嘅就係同身邊嘅老人家/新移民講<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">著數照拎 拒投建制</span></span><br />\n建制輸得愈慘，佢地就會令更多著數黎呃班新移民同老人家<br />\n[/red]我地係要說服到呢班人由建制轉過黎投泛民，每多1票跳槽，前後就差2票[red]<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">立法會一定要有7成，甚至8成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命<br />\n黎明來到要光復這香港<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"00507cd4274a5e7f1c609443b8ac666e9ee367bc","tid":1754111,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T06:07:05.000Z","msg":"（twitter戰線)國際都關注今次香港的區選<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1754022\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1754022</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">出門之前 rt like reply</span><br />\nTwitter組24小時keep住更新<br />\n幫手retweet<br />\n㩒入👉<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBo